{"tid":272403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[填詞人] 大家點睇 小克 (蔣子軒) ?","createTime":"2017-06-05T19:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T06:31:13.000Z","uid":66938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ccc70d0e5ee5ed751809ebdc8c07db0d4b95218d","tid":272403,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T19:17:38.000Z","msg":"填詞人, 林夕,黃偉文 大家就講得多<br />\n林夕徒弟 林若寧 大家都有討論過<br />\n但好似唔見人討論下小克 (蔣子軒)<br />\n<br />\n幾鐘意小克D詞,<br />\n唔會太堆砌feel, 但又唔會好似黃偉文個d咁直白<br />\n就算只係普通既文字,句子, 小克既詞一樣令人有反思既空間<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得小克 可以話係 黃偉文 同 林夕 既中間<br />\n玄得黎唔會難明, 直白得黎又帶點詩意<br />\n<br />\n另外 小克x 周國賢 可以話係必有佳作<br />\n好似 有時 三部曲<br />\n<br />\n有時 重逢 星塵<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=op0Mr0ncPYg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dop0Mr0ncPYg&d=Rq9gFWrYpwVjoItm5vmgSTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=bf930294\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=op0Mr0ncPYg</a><br />\n<br />\n個人最鐘意星塵<br />\n第一次覺得音樂原來真係可以做到宇宙個種浩瀚既感覺<br />\n亦第一次發現原來廣東話一樣可以寫出無邊宇宙既空虛感<br />\n星塵 個七分鐘真係好似宇宙漂流左幾個世紀咁<br />\n<br />\n另外第二首鐘意係 eason 既 四季<br />\n個人覺得呢個有人既mv好似有feel d<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3aZS7On4etw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3aZS7On4etw&d=Rq9gFWrYpwVjoItm5vmgSTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=22b29fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3aZS7On4etw</a><br />\n<br />\n最後送上都係佢既作品<br />\n張繼聰 - 生命之花<br />\n生命之花一定要聽夫妻合唱版<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=soEVL7qhePQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsoEVL7qhePQ&d=Rq9gFWrYpwVjoItm5vmgSTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a7af1adb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=soEVL7qhePQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張敬軒 - 靈魂相認<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PZSp9mTgx6E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPZSp9mTgx6E&d=Rq9gFWrYpwVjoItm5vmgSTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=436a0e8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PZSp9mTgx6E</a>"},{"pid":"7f78672852ea4c1482b34dac93cbdbd5eb9a6fd7","tid":272403,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T19:25:13.000Z","msg":"講少少小克既個人資料啦<br />\n小克 真名叫 蔣子軒<br />\n1974年 出身,  今年都43了<br />\npoly 仔 設計系<br />\n<br />\n小克老婆叫 阮筠庭, 今年37歲<br />\n係大陸既著名畫家黎, 插畫,漫畫都有 (小克都有畫 漫畫)<br />\n佢老婆都好靚女下<br />\n同埋畫d 畫都靚,好文藝,詩情畫意個種"},{"pid":"4d0bc518335223d0a1c8ef61995fc994639f15e6","tid":272403,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:22:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79a034f0bd85575f90c65f1f088efa1992c0aedd","tid":272403,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:31:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37051eda248c90c1c35586097f54b082c94ae2dd","tid":272403,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:13:03.000Z","msg":"無人理cry"},{"pid":"26eeb707db8597f47bf49d40c29c891f76375568","tid":272403,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識貨"},{"pid":"c724146a8325151a95b8b012ac5cc72e07de29dc","tid":272403,"uid":50535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"這邊廂那邊廂系列 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8f03be704c405fdb3b931584b13be90cdef4a6","tid":272403,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:19:52.